tar xvzf proftpd-1.2.0pre7.tar.gz
cp proftpd-ldap.patch proftpd-1.2.0pre7
cd proftpd-1.2.0pre7
patch -sp1 < proftpd-ldap.patch
./configure --with-modules=mod_ldap
make
make install
Add the contents of the 'schema' file to your slapd.oc.conf.
The 'ldif' file contains a sample ldif. Modify it to your liking and
    say ldapadd -D your-root-dn -w your-root-dn-password < ldif
